app_description: People who keep journals have life twice. Jessamine West My Thoughts makes it easy and safe to keep your diary. Features: Pincode and FaceID TouchID for protecting your diary Simple and intuitive interface Add photos to your diary entries Add a mood to your diary entries Suggestions to note depends on your visit places Sync via iCloud between all your devices. Your entries won t get lost even if you change your device. Automatic emotion recognition based on the entered text for languages: English Spanish German French No ads. Not at all.
